OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry this
OL,6,Fevening with some late sunshine,
OL,7,Fthough cloudier along Caithness coast.
OL,8,FThen the rest of the night will be
OL,9,Fdry, clear periods, but some low cloud
OL,10,Fdeveloping near the Moray Firth and
OL,11,Faround the Minches.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FDry with long spells of
OL,14,Fsunshine for most, but patchy low
OL,15,Fcloud may linger along North Sea
OL,16,Fcoasts and coastal parts of the
OL,17,Fnorthwest. Very warm or hot inland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
