OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fstart Friday otherwise dry and sunny,
OL,7,Ffar north remaining cloudy. Cloudy
OL,8,Fstart on Saturday, chance of a light
OL,9,Fshower, then sunny. Sunday starting
OL,10,Fsunny then clouding over. Cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
